                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="67ra" to="76vb1"/>
                     <title>Unidentified letter attributed to Evagrius Ponticus, addressed to his monk-brothers</title>
                     <note>A letter attributed to <persName ref="PRS3921Evagrius"/>.</note>
                     <incipit>በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="MK"/> ጸሓፍነ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ በቍዔት፡ እምድርሳነ፡ ባሕሉ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ አባ፡ ወግሪስ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="MK"/> አእምር፡ ኦአኃው፡ ፍቁር፡ እስመ፡ አፍቅሮተ፡ ዛቲ፡ ዓለም፡
                        ተሀውክ፡ ልበ፡ ወታጸልም፡ ንጻሬ፡ ወታርኅቅ፡ እምእግዚአብሔር፡ ልዑል። አንተኒ፡ ኦአኃው፡ ግድፍ፡ እምኔከ፡ ወኢትፀመድ፡ ለፍትወት፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="MK"/></incipit>
                     <note> cf. <ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient754#p1_i7.4"/> and <ref type="mss" corresp="EMML1387"/> <locus from="84b" to="86b"/>. 
                        It seems unlikely that the text is to be identified with <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2471ToEulo"/> as is proposed in <ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient754#p1_i7.4"/>.</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
