                           the sections of <ref target="#ms_i2"/>; supplication formula on <locus target="#118rb"/>; word <foreign xml:lang="gez">salām</foreign>
                           ‘salutation’ and its abbreviations in <ref target="#ms_i7"/>, <ref target="#ms_i12"/> and <ref target="#ms_i13"/>; phrases
                           <foreign xml:lang="gez">ba-sagid sǝbḥat</foreign> ‘through prostration, glory’ and <foreign xml:lang="gez">maḥarit</foreign> ‘merciful’
